m spanning our truth‑seeking frontier model Grok, AI solutions for consumer and enterprise customers, X—our real‑time information, entertainment, and free speech platform—and AI computational infrastructure.”*  \n*(Also: “operates a vertically integrated AI platform spanning a frontier LLM Grok, AI solutions for consumer and enterprise customers, X — a real‑time information, entertainment, and free speech platform — and AI computational infrastructure.”)*\n\nThe AI segment encompasses:\n- **Grok** – a frontier large language model (LLM) and consumer/enterprise AI assistant (including features such as Grok Voice, Grok Imagine, and Grok Teams).\n- **X platform** – a real‑time information, entertainment, and free‑speech platform that integrates AI tools.\n- **AI compute infrastructure** – the vertically built data‑center and computational resources that power both Grok and the AI‑enabled features of X.\n\n---\n\nAll three segments operate as a vertically integrated innovation engine, with the Connectivity and AI segments expected to be the primary drivers of near‑term revenue growth.',
